data.value: select "MstEmployee"."Id", "MstEmployee"."BiometricIdNumber", "MstEmployee"."FullName", "MstEmployee"."Address", "MstEmployee"."CellphoneNumber", "MstEmployee"."DateOfBirth", "MstEmployee"."PlaceOfBirth", "MstEmployee"."DateHired", "MstEmployee"."CivilStatus", "MstEmployee"."Sex", "MstPosition"."Position", "MstDepartment"."Department", "MstCitizenship"."Citizenship", "MstReligion"."Religion" from (((("dbo"."MstEmployee" "MstEmployee" inner join "dbo"."MstDepartment" "MstDepartment" on ("MstDepartment"."Id" = "MstEmployee"."DepartmentId")) inner join "dbo"."MstCitizenship" "MstCitizenship" on ("MstCitizenship"."Id" = "MstEmployee"."CitizenshipId")) inner join "dbo"."MstReligion" "MstReligion" on ("MstReligion"."Id" = "MstEmployee"."ReligionId")) inner join "dbo"."MstPosition" "MstPosition" on ("MstPosition"."Id" = "MstEmployee"."PositionId")) where ("MstEmployee"."Id" = @ParamId)
